			<MudItem xs="7" Style="padding-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 40px" Class="border">
				<MudText Style="color: #333333; font-size: 20px; font-family: 'Noto Serif', serif; font-weight: 700;">CRI completes more than 500,000 calls per month from our in-house full-service contact center, providing leading solutions and services to industries around the globe.</MudText>
